<date month='October' day='30' year='2017' />

<abstract><t>Multipath TCP has shown how a reliable transport protocol can efficiently use multiple paths for a given connection.  We leverage the experience gained with Multipath TCP to propose simple extensions that enable QUIC to efficiently use multiple paths during the lifetime of a QUIC connection.</t></abstract>

